docs.abstract: The league had largely avoided fan furor over this season, but disputed calls in Sunday’s two thrilling conference championship games brought it right back.
docs.snippet: The league had largely avoided fan furor over this season, but disputed calls in Sunday’s two thrilling conference championship games brought it right back.
docs.lead_paragraph: KANSAS CITY, Mo. — The N.F.L. this season finally appeared to have accomplished its goal of “getting back to football” after several years of off-field turmoil that ranged from player misconduct to weekly protests during the national anthem. But the league’s bounce-back season was knocked off stride on Sunday, as officials in the two conference championship games made baffling, controversial calls that to some degree overshadowed the otherwise thrilling matchups.

headline.main: The N.F.L. Confronts More Controversy, This Time on the Field
headline.print_headline: The Squads Creating  The Loudest Buzz?  They Wear Stripes

docs.abstract: Rewriting its slogan as “Is this the best a man can get?”, the razor brand presented examples of toxic masculinity, earning itself both celebrity praise and calls for a boycott.
docs.snippet: Rewriting its slogan as “Is this the best a man can get?”, the razor brand presented examples of toxic masculinity, earning itself both celebrity praise and calls for a boycott.
docs.lead_paragraph: In less than two minutes, the men and boys in Gillette’s new ad engage in a panoply of bad behavior: bullying, fighting, discrimination, sexual harassment and more. A line of them, standing behind smoke wafting up from their grills, recites, “Boys will be boys will be boys will be boys.”

headline.main: Gillette Ad With a #MeToo Edge Attracts Support and Outrage

docs.lead_paragraph: During an interview with the comedian Kevin Hart broadcast on Friday, Ellen DeGeneres offered a lengthy defense of Hart and said that she called someone at the Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences to request that he be reinstated as Oscars host. Almost a month ago, Hart stepped down from that role after a backlash over past comments he had made that were considered homophobic.

headline.main: Ellen DeGeneres: Academy Should Reinstate Kevin Hart as Oscars Host

docs.abstract: The making of Sheila Pree Bright’s photo-mural of black women who had lost their sons gave a group of mothers a chance to tell their stories.
docs.snippet: The making of Sheila Pree Bright’s photo-mural of black women who had lost their sons gave a group of mothers a chance to tell their stories.
docs.lead_paragraph: The past informs the present in the work of Sheila Pree Bright, who has been photographing the Black Lives Matter movement since 2014. As an artist who draws connections between today’s young activists and their civil rights forebears, she seemed a natural choice to be among 11 socially conscious artists selected to create murals highlighting Atlanta’s past, present and future in time for the Super Bowl, when the city will be in the spotlight.

headline.main: From the Civil Rights Movement to Black Lives Matter: Honoring Black Mothers Who Lost Their Sons
